{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set in 1930s Southern Europe, where technology has eclipsed magic, an estranged group of Moon Worshippers known as the Anaxagori resurfaces with an ominous prophecy: an eternal lunar eclipse. Dismissed by the public as antiquated mystics, the Anaxagori's warnings contrast sharply with the populace's enthusiasm for what is hailed as a historic celestial event. Fresh from an archaeological expedition, Helena Nightshade only learns of the eclipse's significance upon arriving in Istanbul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/nho1_gif1.gif?t=1730783087\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Initially drawn by the thrill of adventure, Helena soon discovers that fate has a hand in her involvement. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2710100/extras/nho1_gif2.gif?t=1730783087\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this point-and-click hidden object adventure game, you will guide Helena as she pieces together clues in her journal, discovers hidden objects throughout her journey, and solves a variety of puzzles and minigames!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore richly detailed scenes, interact with intriguing characters, become friends with a certain avian, and aid the right forces to prevent the cataclysmic tragedy!</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Moonrise","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710100/c0f0880d33eb99b849d4ff041587b31d2897a7a7.jpg"},{"name":"Fated Reunion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2710100/6ab9457e39b653789795ada45bd86592986da229.jpg"},{"name":"Prophetic Revelation","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamc